ğŸ†• Add New Patient with Priority Insert patients into the queue by specifying their name and priority level (e.g., Emergency or Regular).

ğŸ”„ Serve Patients in Correct Order Ensures that patients are removed from the queue in such a way that emergency patients are always served before regular ones.

ğŸ“‹ Display All Patients in Queue Shows the current state of the queue so users can clearly see which patients are waiting and their priority status.

